  "original_title": "\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9c\u0db8\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A conflict between two Jaffna villages",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that seven houses have been damaged in a conflict between two villages in the Pedurutuduwa area of \u200b\u200bJaffna. The clash has been on and off for four days",
        "The police have arrested two people in connection with this conflict and the police have started investigations to find 25 other suspects involved in the incident.",
        "Swords and stones were hurled and the Nelliady police have received about seven complaints regarding the conflict, the police say.",
        "Accordingly, the police and the police special task force have been deployed in the area to maintain peace in the area and the police have started investigations to find the suspects involved in the conflict."
      ],
